snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: Ronth| Official Trailer| Dileesh Pothan, Roshan Mathew| Directed by Shahi Kabir| In Cinemas 13 June
snippet.description:
A gripping cop drama which follows a stoic senior police officer haunted by his past and his idealistic young partner assigned to night patrols. Their clashing personalities ignite tension, but as a series of intense and emotional events unfold, a reluctant bond begins to form. When a life-threatening incident threatens their careers, both must confront their deepest fears and darkest truths to survive the shadows of duty.


Genre - Drama

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Forgotten Malayalam Movies S06 E01 | Radio | Malayalam Movie Review Funny | Thalaivasal VJ
snippet.description:
Forgotten Malayalam Movies is a movie review series where we review some of the greatest (read : worst) movies in malayalam.

This season's first movie is Radio. Radio was released on Mother's day 2013 and was a knockout blockbuster, destroying all its competitors by a huge margin. Radio was the inspiration for a number of movies like Paa (Bollywood) and The Curious Case Of Benjamin Button (Hollywood). snippet.title: 🔥 SPOKEN ENGLISH CLASS 1 | ENGLISH SPEAKING COURSE | LEARN FLUENTLY |SPEAKING PRACTICE FOR BEGINNERS
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE TO OUR NEW ENGLISH SPEAKING PLATFORM: @dearsirenglishspeaking 

ENGLISH SPEAKING TEST: https://forms.gle/9ZMcsi3RoZDPsTq9A

Welcome to your first class of our Spoken English Course, designed specifically for beginners who want to speak English fluently and confidently. In this session, we are covering all the basics of English speaking along with live speaking practice to help you start using English in real-life situations from day one.

This is not just a theory class — we believe in practice-based learning. That’s why this session includes English speaking exercises and daily English conversation practice to build your fluency step by step.

At the end of the class, we’ve included a test for spoken English learners. It’s a structured test to identify exactly where learners are weak, so we can plan our future spoken English classes more effectively, focusing on those specific areas.

ENGLISH SPEAKING TEST: https://forms.gle/9ZMcsi3RoZDPsTq9A

We’ve also launched a separate platform for Spoken English learning as well, where learners can access a full library of spoken English lectures, along with exclusive sessions on personality development, interview preparation, and public speaking. This is independent of our YouTube content and offers a more focused and advanced learning environment.

SUBSCRIBE TO NEW ENGLISH SPEAKING PLATFORM:  @dearsirenglishspeaking  

Ideal for:

* Beginners learning English speaking
* Students preparing for interviews in English
* Anyone who wants to improve fluency with structured practice
* Learners looking for basic to advanced spoken English training

Take the test https://forms.gle/9ZMcsi3RoZDPsTq9A , follow the classes, and track your improvement as we move forward.

Don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe for more high-quality English speaking practice videos and updates on our exclusive learning platform.

snippet.title: யார்மேலயோ உள்ள கோவத்த உன்கிட்ட காட்டிட்டேன் மனசில ஒன்னும் வச்சிக்காதடா | Aanandham |Super Good Films
snippet.description:
"I showed the anger I had on someone else to you… Don’t take it to heart, da."
This heart-touching dialogue from the Tamil family drama Aanandham beautifully captures the raw emotions in relationships. Starring Murali, Mammootty, Rambha, and Devyani, the film is a Super Good Films production that resonates with love, forgiveness, and family bonds.

Relive this emotional moment that showcases the brilliance of Tamil cinema in expressing feelings that words often fail to.

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Panetar Parka Na Odhiya | પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢ્યા | New Gujarati Bewafa Song 2025
snippet.description:
Check out the new Gujarati bewafa song by Rakesh Barot, "Panetar Parka Na Odhiya" only on   @SaregamaGujarati  💔🎶

રાકેશ બારોટનું નવું ગુજરાતી બેવફા ગીત "પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢ્યા" સાંભળો, માત્ર  @SaregamaGujarati  પર.

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Lyrics: Prakash Vaghela 
Music: Dipesh chavada 
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Sweta Sen, Bobby Kalpesh 
Co.artist: Lata Prajapati, Dharati Patel, Sharmaji 
Dop: Arvind Motap 
Camera Attended: Kartik Thakor 
Editing: Kishor Rajput 
Concept & Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenis Talaviya
Spot boys: Kiran Thakor, Lalo, Ajay
Makeup: Hasmukh limbachiya 
Hair Style: Bhavana Ben
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot
Ass.director: Babusinh Thakor
Poster design: Aman Agola
Junior Artist Management: Nayan Thakor
Production Management: Jigar Panchal 
Food Management: Village Vila cafe 
Thanks: Manish Patel, Divyang patel

Lyrics:
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨)
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા 
આજ અડધા રસ્તે સાથ તે છોડયા ..
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
જીવતિ લાશ બનાવી ને છોડી રે જવના 
તારા ગયા પછી અમે નોધારા થવાના 
મારા હાચવેલાં દિલ ને તમે તોડીયા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
હો શેતર ના શેઢે રોજ મને મળવા આવતી 
તને નઈ ભૂલું એવા સોંગંધ ખાતીતી 
હો ચોરી યે ચઢતા જીવ કેમ ચાલીયો 
તારો રયો ના ખોળિયા માં પ્રાણ અમારો 
એની ઉપર તારી ચોરીયો ચીતરાવી 
અમે અમારા હાલ પર રોય 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા ……
હો પારકા ના હાથ મા હાથ સે તમારો 
જોઈ એને બેવફા જીવ બળે મારો 
હો નજર સોમુ ફેરા ફરે ચમનું જોયું જાય રે
 નથી જવાતું મારા દિલમાં દર્દ થાય રે 
હો ખુશીયોને  તે ઠોકર રે ચઢાવી 
આખરે બેવફા તારી જાત રે બતાવી 
મારી જિંદગી મા ઝેર તે ધોળ્યા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા….

localized.title: Rakesh Barot | Panetar Parka Na Odhiya | પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢ્યા | New Gujarati Bewafa Song 2025
localized.description:
Check out the new Gujarati bewafa song by Rakesh Barot, "Panetar Parka Na Odhiya" only on   @SaregamaGujarati  💔🎶

રાકેશ બારોટનું નવું ગુજરાતી બેવફા ગીત "પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢ્યા" સાંભળો, માત્ર  @SaregamaGujarati  પર.

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Lyrics: Prakash Vaghela 
Music: Dipesh chavada 
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Sweta Sen, Bobby Kalpesh 
Co.artist: Lata Prajapati, Dharati Patel, Sharmaji 
Dop: Arvind Motap 
Camera Attended: Kartik Thakor 
Editing: Kishor Rajput 
Concept & Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenis Talaviya
Spot boys: Kiran Thakor, Lalo, Ajay
Makeup: Hasmukh limbachiya 
Hair Style: Bhavana Ben
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot
Ass.director: Babusinh Thakor
Poster design: Aman Agola
Junior Artist Management: Nayan Thakor
Production Management: Jigar Panchal 
Food Management: Village Vila cafe 
Thanks: Manish Patel, Divyang patel

Lyrics:
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨)
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા 
આજ અડધા રસ્તે સાથ તે છોડયા ..
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
જીવતિ લાશ બનાવી ને છોડી રે જવના 
તારા ગયા પછી અમે નોધારા થવાના 
મારા હાચવેલાં દિલ ને તમે તોડીયા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
હો શેતર ના શેઢે રોજ મને મળવા આવતી 
તને નઈ ભૂલું એવા સોંગંધ ખાતીતી 
હો ચોરી યે ચઢતા જીવ કેમ ચાલીયો 
તારો રયો ના ખોળિયા માં પ્રાણ અમારો 
એની ઉપર તારી ચોરીયો ચીતરાવી 
અમે અમારા હાલ પર રોય 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા ……
હો પારકા ના હાથ મા હાથ સે તમારો 
જોઈ એને બેવફા જીવ બળે મારો 
હો નજર સોમુ ફેરા ફરે ચમનું જોયું જાય રે
 નથી જવાતું મારા દિલમાં દર્દ થાય રે 
હો ખુશીયોને  તે ઠોકર રે ચઢાવી 
આખરે બેવફા તારી જાત રે બતાવી 
મારી જિંદગી મા ઝેર તે ધોળ્યા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા….

Witness the heartwarming story of brotherhood and family values in "Om Jai Jagadish." Released in 2002, this Hindi film beautifully portrays the lives of three brothers and their unwavering bond despite facing various trials and tribulations. When their father passes away, the eldest brother, Om, selflessly takes on the responsibility of caring for his younger siblings, Jai and Jagadish. As they navigate life's challenges, including financial difficulties and personal aspirations, their unity is tested. Will their strong familial love withstand the pressures of the outside world? Experience a captivating narrative filled with emotion, drama, and memorable performances from a stellar cast.

◾ Film : Om Jai Jagadish.
◾ Director : Anupam Kher.
◾ Producer : Vashu Bhagnani.
◾ Cast : Anil Kapoor, Fardeen Khan, Abhishek Bachchan, Mahima Chaudhry, Urmila Matondkar, Pooja Batra.

Welcome to our deep-dive analysis of Housefull 5 Box Office Collection Worldwide! In this video, we break down the Housefull 5 Total Collection across both domestic and international markets. From the much-hyped Housefull 5 1st Day Collection to its overall performance, we’ve got all the numbers to show how this star-packed comedy thriller is faring globally.

Directed by Tarun Mansukhani and produced by Sajid Nadiadwala under Nadiadwala Grandson Entertainment, Housefull 5 features a massive ensemble: Akshay Kumar, Riteish Deshmukh, Abhishek Bachchan, Sanjay Dutt, Jacqueline Fernandez, Nargis Fakhri, and more. With a reported Housefull 5 Movie Budget of around ₹375 crores, it’s among the biggest Bollywood comedies ever made.

But is it living up to the hype? Our Housefull 5 Movie Review explores the film’s comedy, chaos, and star power. We’ll also look at whether Housefull 5 can break franchise records and become a blockbuster of 2025.

From grand visuals to a suspense-filled cruise setting, this video covers:
- Housefull 5 India & overseas collections
- Housefull 5 Budget vs. earnings
- Comparison with previous Housefull films
- Housefull 5 Public reactions & critic reviews

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: BANANA BAJJI | Banana Fry | Valakkai Bajji Recipe  Cooking in Village | Tasty Plantain Evening Snack
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we made a delicious and crispy Banana Bajji using raw plantains, also known as Valakkai Bajji in Tamil. This traditional South Indian snack, especially in Kerala and Tamil Nadu, is a perfect evening treat, especially when served hot with tea. We sliced fresh plantains, dipped them in a flavorful gram flour batter seasoned with spices, and deep-fried them over a woodfire stove until golden and crisp.

Our village-style cooking brings out the authentic taste and aroma of this simple yet tasty snack. Watch how we prepare these bajjis in a natural outdoor setting, using fresh ingredients and traditional methods.

Enjoy the satisfying crunch and soft banana filling in every bite! Perfect for family gatherings or as a festive snack.

de-DE.title: BANANEN-BAJI | Bananen-Pommes | Valakkai Bajji-Rezept Kochen im Dorf | Leckerer Abendsnack mit Ko...
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf ein köstliches und knuspriges Bananen-Bajji aus rohen Kochbananen zubereitet, auf Tamil auch Valakkai Bajji genannt. Dieser traditionelle südindische Snack, vor allem in Kerala und Tamil Nadu, ist ein perfekter Abendgenuss, besonders heiß serviert mit Tee. Wir haben frische Kochbananen in Scheiben geschnitten, sie in einen aromatischen Kichererbsenmehlteig getaucht und über einem Holzofen frittiert, bis sie goldbraun und knusprig waren.

Unsere dörfliche Küche bringt den authentischen Geschmack und das Aroma dieses einfachen, aber leckeren Snacks perfekt zur Geltung. Sehen Sie zu, wie wir diese Bajjis in der Natur mit frischen Zutaten und nach traditionellen Methoden zubereiten.

Genießen Sie das köstliche Knuspern und die weiche Bananenfüllung mit jedem Bissen! Perfekt für Familienfeiern oder als festlicher Snack.

it.title: BAJI DI BANANE | Frittura di banane | Ricetta Valakkai Bajji Cucinare nel villaggio | Delizioso s...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo preparato un delizioso e croccante Banana Bajji usando platani crudi, noto anche come Valakkai Bajji in Tamil. Questo spuntino tradizionale dell'India meridionale, in particolare del Kerala e del Tamil Nadu, è una delizia perfetta per la sera, soprattutto se servito caldo con il tè. Abbiamo affettato platani freschi, li abbiamo immersi in una saporita pastella di farina di ceci condita con spezie e li abbiamo fritti su una stufa a legna fino a quando non sono diventati dorati e croccanti.

La nostra cucina in stile villaggio esalta il gusto e l'aroma autentici di questo spuntino semplice ma gustoso. Guarda come prepariamo questi bajji in un ambiente naturale all'aperto, utilizzando ingredienti freschi e metodi tradizionali.

Gusta la croccantezza appagante e il morbido ripieno di banana in ogni boccone! Perfetto per le riunioni di famiglia o come spuntino festivo.

hi.title: केले की बाजी | केला फ्राई | गांव में वलक्कई बज्जी पकाने की विधि | स्वादिष्ट केला शाम का नाश्ता
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने कच्चे केलों का उपयोग करके एक स्वादिष्ट और कुरकुरी केले की बाजी बनाई, जिसे तमिल में वलाक्काई बाजी भी कहा जाता है। यह पारंपरिक दक्षिण भारतीय नाश्ता, विशेष रूप से केरल और तमिलनाडु में, शाम के खाने के लिए एकदम सही है, खासकर जब इसे चाय के साथ गरमागरम परोसा जाए। हमने ताज़े केलों को काटा, उन्हें मसालों से भरे स्वादिष्ट बेसन के घोल में डुबोया और लकड़ी की आग पर सुनहरा और कुरकुरा होने तक डीप फ्राई किया।

हमारे गांव-शैली के खाना पकाने से इस सरल लेकिन स्वादिष्ट नाश्ते का असली स्वाद और सुगंध सामने आती है। देखें कि हम इन बाजी को प्राकृतिक बाहरी सेटिंग में, ताज़ी सामग्री और पारंपरिक तरीकों का उपयोग करके कैसे तैयार करते हैं।

हर निवाले में संतोषजनक कुरकुरेपन और नरम केले की फिलिंग का आनंद लें! पारिवारिक समारोहों या उत्सव के नाश्ते के लिए एकदम सही।

ja.title: バナナバジ |バナナフライ | Valakkai Bajji レシピ 村で料理 |おいしいプランテンの夕方のおやつ
ja.description:
今日は私たちの村で、生のプランテンを使った、美味しくてサクサクのバナナ・バジを作りました。タミル語ではヴァラッカイ・バジとも呼ばれています。南インド、特にケーララ州とタミル・ナードゥ州でよく食べられるこの伝統的なスナックは、温かいお茶と一緒に食べると、夕方の楽しみにぴったりです。新鮮なプランテンをスライスし、スパイスで味付けした風味豊かなひよこ豆の粉の衣につけて、薪ストーブでこんがりと焼き色がつくまで揚げます。

私たちの村流の調理法は、このシンプルながらも美味しいスナックの本物の味と香りを引き立てます。自然の恵み豊かな屋外で、新鮮な食材と伝統的な製法を使ってバジを作る様子をご覧ください。

一口ごとに、満足感のあるサクサクとした食感と、ふわふわのバナナフィリングをお楽しみください！家族の集まりやお祝いのスナックに最適です。

id.title: PISANG BAJI | Gorengan Pisang | Resep Masakan Valakkai Bajji di Desa | Camilan Lezat Malam Hari d...
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami membuat Bajji Pisang yang lezat dan renyah menggunakan pisang mentah, yang juga dikenal sebagai Valakkai Bajji dalam bahasa Tamil. Camilan tradisional India Selatan ini, khususnya di Kerala dan Tamil Nadu, merupakan sajian malam yang sempurna, terutama jika disajikan hangat dengan teh. Kami mengiris pisang segar, mencelupkannya ke dalam adonan tepung gram yang beraroma dan dibumbui dengan rempah-rempah, dan menggorengnya di atas tungku kayu bakar hingga berwarna keemasan dan renyah.

Cara memasak ala desa kami menghasilkan rasa dan aroma asli dari camilan sederhana namun lezat ini. Saksikan cara kami menyiapkan bajji ini di alam terbuka, menggunakan bahan-bahan segar dan metode tradisional.

Nikmati kerenyahan yang memuaskan dan isian pisang yang lembut di setiap gigitan! Sempurna untuk acara kumpul keluarga atau sebagai camilan hari raya.

es-US.title: PLÁTANO BAJI | Plátano frito Receta de Valakkai Bajji cocinando en el pueblo | Deliciosa merienda...
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, preparamos un delicioso y crujiente Bajji de Plátano con plátanos crudos, también conocido como Valakkai Bajji en tamil. Este aperitivo tradicional del sur de la India, especialmente en Kerala y Tamil Nadu, es un capricho perfecto para la tarde, sobre todo caliente con té. Cortamos plátanos frescos en rodajas, los sumergimos en una sabrosa masa de harina de garbanzos sazonada con especias y los freímos en una estufa de leña hasta que quedaron dorados y crujientes.

Nuestra cocina al estilo del pueblo realza el auténtico sabor y aroma de este sencillo pero delicioso aperitivo. Observa cómo preparamos estos bajjis en un entorno natural al aire libre, con ingredientes frescos y métodos tradicionales.

¡Disfruta de su delicioso crujido y suave relleno de plátano en cada bocado! Perfecto para reuniones familiares o como aperitivo festivo.

pt-BR.title: BANANA BAJI | Banana Frita | Receita de Valakkai Bajji cozinhando na vila | Lanche da noite sabor...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, preparamos um delicioso e crocante Bajji de Banana usando bananas-da-terra cruas, também conhecido como Valakkai Bajji em tâmil. Este lanche tradicional do sul da Índia, especialmente em Kerala e Tamil Nadu, é um deleite perfeito para a noite, principalmente quando servido quente com chá. Fatiamos bananas-da-terra frescas, mergulhamos em uma saborosa massa de farinha de grão-de-bico temperada com especiarias e as fritamos em um fogão a lenha até dourarem e ficarem crocantes.

Nossa culinária típica da aldeia realça o sabor e o aroma autênticos deste lanche simples, porém saboroso. Veja como preparamos estes bajjis em um ambiente natural ao ar livre, usando ingredientes frescos e métodos tradicionais.

Aprecie a crocância e o recheio macio de banana em cada mordida! Perfeito para reuniões familiares ou como um lanche festivo.

fr-FR.title: BAJI À LA BANANE | Frites de bananes | Recette de Valakkai Bajji Cuisiner dans le village | Savou...
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons préparé un délicieux et croustillant bajji à la banane avec des plantains crus, aussi appelé Valakkai Bajji en tamoul. Ce plat traditionnel du sud de l'Inde, notamment au Kerala et au Tamil Nadu, est un régal idéal en soirée, surtout servi chaud avec du thé. Nous avons coupé des plantains frais en tranches, les avons trempés dans une savoureuse pâte à base de farine de pois chiche et assaisonnée d'épices, puis les avons frits au feu de bois jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient dorés et croustillants.

Notre cuisine villageoise met en valeur le goût et l'arôme authentiques de ce plat simple et savoureux. Découvrez comment nous préparons ces bajjis en plein air, avec des ingrédients frais et des méthodes traditionnelles.

Savourez le croquant et la douceur de la banane à chaque bouchée ! Parfait pour les réunions de famille ou pour un goûter festif.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: Vilen - Bad Trip (Official Video)
snippet.description:
‘BT' is a song about a rugged, tough guy drinking away his sorrows, his red, bloodshot eyes revealing a troubled past. Today, he's not to be messed with, as he is possibly missing an old love.


Artist : Vilen
Lyrcist : Vilen
Music : Vilen
Composer : Vilen
Director : Vilen
Screenplay : Vilen
Editor : Vilen
Colour correction : Vilen
DOP : Alex
Mix Master : Hanish Taneja
Music production : Vilen, Maniac
Recording studio : G10 Studio
Label : Darks Music Company
Starring : Vilen, BigSsmoke, Amit Om Malik, Akhil Rathee, Nitin Dabas
Location courtesy : Mnky Houz, Privee Delhi

Lyrics -
Ho ankh chadh ri ho ri kasuti laal
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

Ho laage aa ri se sajan ki re yaad
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

Ho ankh chadh ri ho ri kasuti laal
Laa ke peg 10 chaale sudha yaar
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se


Darr jaga chore ki re ankh dekh le
Makha ankh dekhle

Kisi laage se jalti aag dekhle
Makha aag dekhle

Laage se bhola aaj
Bhairav ka roop se le rhaya

2-4 bhaari bhaari
Gelyan yo bhoot bhi le rhaya

Chore hat hat ke chaale
Chori masta rahi se

Aaj suhaati na jo
Aankh matka rahi se

Aaja mardaan ke bhi halaat dekhle
Re halaat dekhle

Tadpe jo saari saari raat dekhle
Aaja raat dekhle


Ho iski kad pe jakham
Haath laal

Taare sir te jo aare se khayaal
Laage se aaj gam mai piwe se


Ho ankh chadh ri ho ri kasuti laal
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

Ho laage aa ri se sajan ki re yaad
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

snippet.description:

snippet.title: आज निर्जला एकादशी की चमत्कारी कथा सुनने से घर में धन सुख शांति और विष्णु लक्ष्मी जी का आगमन होता है
snippet.description:
Nirjala Ekadashi " निर्जला एकादशी ' :-
निर्जला एकादशी हिंदू धर्म में सबसे शक्तिशाली दिनों में से एक है। निर्जला एकादशी पूरी तरह से भगवान विष्णु की पूजा के लिए समर्पित है और इसे सबसे पवित्र दिनों में से एक माना जाता है। इस शुभ दिन भगवान विष्णु और मां लक्ष्मी की विशेष पूजा-अर्चना करने का विधान है। मान्यता है इस व्रत को करने से साधक को शुभ फल की प्राप्ति होती है। साथ ही जीवन में सुख-शांति बनी रहती है।

snippet.title: Tata Harrier EV AWD First Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Tata Motors finally launched their first AWD SUV in the last 5 years, Harrier.ev. It is an electric SUV that comes with Dual Motor. Tata Motors call it QWD or Qual Wheel drive. Harrier Electric will also come with RWD single motor setup as standard. The starting price of the Harrier electric 65 kWh RWD base variant is Rs 21.49 Lakh Ex-Showroom. The other battery pack is 75 kWh. This car can do 0-100 in just 6.3 seconds in Dual motor AWD trim and should give a practical range of up to 480 km in RWD single motor variant.

snippet.title: EMI-ൽ മുങ്ങി മലയാളികൾ! രക്ഷപ്പെടാൻ ഇങ്ങനെ ചെയ്യൂ! Loan EMI Trap Explained | Sharique Samsudheen
snippet.description:
ഒരു Capital, രണ്ടു Returns എങ്ങനെ എന്ന്മ നസിലാക്കാൻ ഈ link ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്യൂ - https://marketfeed.me/automate_sharique

In this video, let's talk about how you can start working towards escaping the loan and debt trap that has captured our generation. This is going to be an in-depth video masterclass on how to escape from loans, different strategies that can be used to become EMI and debt-free. We will discuss conventional strategies like avalanche and snowball debt repayment methods in Malayalam, but then also go into better strategies that can help you pay loans faster. So make sure you watch the video till the very end - it is going to be useful for your entire life.

Welcome to a Sharique Samsudheen video, explained in Malayalam! 🚀

🔗 Links in this video 
1. Loan Calculator Excel Sheet - https://marketfeed.me/debt_calculator
2. EMI Calculator Link - https://marketfeed.me/emi_calculator

00:00 Current Life Situation of Many Malayalis - Loan and EMI Trap
05:45 Problems Summarised and Agenda of the video
07:40 2 Hidden Realities Behind How Loans are Designed
12:00 Step 1 - Get Clarity of current situation. How much loan is too much?
16:33 Step 2 - Optimise your Loans using these strategies 
22:18 Step 3 - How to find extra money in life for Kerala
27:00 Step 4 - Repayment Strategies for loans 
29:30 My favourite strategy for loan repayment

snippet.description:
Join us on a heartfelt journey from a high-profile event with Errol Musk (father of Elon Musk) at the Taj Hotel to the grand wedding reception of India’s beloved educator, Khan Sir in Patna! 💍✨

In this exclusive vlog-style episode, we witness the blend of leadership, humility, and inspiration. From late-night dinners with global guests to catching the last flight to attend Khan Sir’s wedding reception — this video showcases the power of relationships, values, and learning from great minds.

🎉 Whether you're inspired by entrepreneurship, leadership, or education revolutionaries, this story will touch your heart. Don't miss the emotional moment with Khan Sir and his newlywed wife, and the reflections on India's rising role in global change!

hi.title: अब तक का सबसे शानदार शतरंज का अंत | गुकेश बनाम मैग्नस कार्लसन | नॉर्वे शतरंज 2025
hi.description:
नॉर्वे शतरंज के पहले राउंड में दुनिया के नंबर 1 मैग्नस कार्लसन और विश्व चैंपियन डी. गुकेश एक दूसरे से भिड़ गए और वह गेम मैग्नस के पक्ष में समाप्त हुआ। अब हम टूर्नामेंट के दूसरे गेम के लिए वापस आ गए हैं, इस बार गुकेश के पास नॉर्वेजियन दिग्गज के खिलाफ सफेद मोहरे हैं। क्या गुकेश अपना बदला ले पाएगा, या मैग्नस एक बार फिर अपनी क्लास दिखाएगा! आईएम सागर शाह की कमेंट्री के साथ इस अद्भुत गेम को देखें और सबसे बेहतरीन शतरंज फिनिश का आनंद लें जिसकी आप कभी उम्मीद कर सकते हैं। वीडियो: चेसबेस इंडिया
आदित्य सुर रॉय और अभ्युदय राम द्वारा शूट किया गया, रवींद्र पोटावाड द्वारा संपादित

snippet.description:

🔹 Special Guests: Secretary, Department of School Education & Literacy (DoSEL), and Joint Secretary, MoE 
🔹 Organized in association with: Ministry of Education (MoE)

This webinar aims to inspire action and awareness among educators, students, and policy makers on the importance of protecting our environment.

#WorldEnvironmentDay #Webinar #MoE #CEE #EnvironmentAwareness #DoSEL #EducationForSustainability

snippet.title: Women ki Duniya | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Welcome to Women Ki Duniya — a hilarious sketch that flips the script on gender roles! 🤯
What if women were the dominant gender in society? In this fun, satirical world, men are the ones being told to “smile more,” struggling to get promoted, and balancing office work and house chores — while women run the show with power, sass, and zero tolerance for mansplaining. 😎💅
From office meetings to family functions, this sketch hilariously reimagines everyday situations with the gender dynamics reversed, making you laugh and think at the same time!
Watch now and enter a world where patriarchy gets a taste of its own medicine! 💥

#WomenKiDuniya #ComedySketch #WhatIfWomenRuled #GenderSwap #Satire #RelatableHumor #WomenPower #DesiSketch #RoleReversal

Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar
